Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.45,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.15,0:00:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.11,0:00:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.24,0:02:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出現在酷一行人面前的少女菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自稱是酷的Fan的她主動為一行人做嚮導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是在前往煌珠樂園的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲蘿發動愛的猛烈攻勢令酷不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候 瑪魯再次前來攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.77,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於是 情急之下菲蘿和酷進行了同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.89,0:02:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第十八唱 虛假的同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.94,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲蘿 你是煌珠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.66,0:02:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先不說這個 現在首要的是打倒敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.43,0:02:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那確實是同契發出的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.22,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我同契感覺不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 快點把敵人幹掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我和酷的愛的必殺技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷和誰同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道是菲蘿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有兩個人的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 這是早安之吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚本想和酷說話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.64,0:04:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不是被希絲卡制止說是太晚了明天再說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 你覺得我怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在問你跟我同契的感想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得是十分默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,氣息一致 也沒有多餘的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷也是這樣認為的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很糟糕是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過因為是第一次也難怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今後多同契幾次的話肯定會好起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那個意思 不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去做早飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起床了嗎 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 把你吵醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 昨天對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和菲蘿同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不 那是因為 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的沒生氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點也不？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.17,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但要是多少吃點醋就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃醋是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去問別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃醋就是喜歡的人 不不 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.30,0:07:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是看到關繫好的朋友\N和別人相處很好時這裏會一下子熱起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很痛苦難受的那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的這裏不熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.14,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等 等等 別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩位 早飯就要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個 這部位是叫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.75,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邊吃邊聽我說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道你聽到了什麼 不過那是個誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我絕對沒有摸蕾的那...那個胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.43,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要說的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲蘿 是關於你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關於我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是擬煌珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚的戰鬥中雖然你跟酷同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但在這煌珠雷達上卻沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.62,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就證明你是擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希絲卡 難道你對菲蘿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被懷疑了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,盯上我們的也是擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼這樣 我和他們不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼為什麼要隱瞞身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 那是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.42,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為想和崇拜的酷同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.86,0:08:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作為酷的Fan的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想和酷同契哪怕一次也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.84,0:08:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己決定走上成為擬煌珠的道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.13,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 這個大陸上的人只把擬煌珠看作道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.94,0:09:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我一直都隱瞞自己是擬煌珠這一身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 昨天我的夢想終於實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.93,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和崇拜的酷合為了一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的話是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.18,0:09:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說這個大陸上的人只把擬煌珠看作道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 我沒有說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真是太慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了能和我同契受了不少苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有 不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能和酷同契就非常滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再來一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天是昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你覺得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關於菲蘿是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她真的只是酷的Fan嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,答案很快就會揭曉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上就到她的村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,預定和她在那裏分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果她是敵人派來的刺客的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.98,0:10:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算到了村子也會編些理由跟著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝旅途一路順風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也要小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另外 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,期待有一天能和你再見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.17,0:11:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無情的告別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不會期待離別之吻什麼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別 別說傻話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來是自尋煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,計劃有變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和他們分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.67,0:11:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,計劃不應該是假扮成酷的Fan 和他們同行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們開始懷疑我的真正身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.16,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到下一個計劃實行之前不繼續監視他們的話可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係 我還有另一手準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次的任務關係到我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這波魯西奧尼大陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從小就被嵌入人造核石的擬煌珠有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於既非人類又非煌珠的我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有一處地方能使我的內心感到平靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在波魯西奧尼大陸擬煌珠只不過是被使用的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.77,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 煌珠不會受到那樣的待遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.08,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成任務之後 你就能高高興興地成為煌珠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 開始新的作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那邊好像無法通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.95,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊的路是「沙漠食人獸」的生存地 禁止通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙漠食人獸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餐後吃的那些東西是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甜品：dessert；沙漠：desert{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.76,0:13:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從名字來看應該是一種生活在這裏的怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.21,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟她分開後一下子安靜了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.15,0:13:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長途旅行或許也需要那種熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.62,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙會繼續隱瞞著擬煌珠的身份生活下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.17,0:14:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 我現在就來救你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.89,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家 沙漠惡魔「沙漠食人獸」已經被我擊退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.31,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲蘿 懷疑你的我真是太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是我們的救命恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何請和我們一起繼續旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我對酷示愛只是為了任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會產生剛才那樣的幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的是太差勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨笨的 不管做什麼都是給大家添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過不是做什麼都很努力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我並不討厭菲蘿你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我究竟是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.25,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要陷進地下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家 我現在就來救你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.28,0:16:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼那孩子會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.35,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回到村裏後我從村長\N那兒得知「沙漠食人獸」的棲息地變動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺得你們或許會遇上麻煩就追了上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.61,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那一大堆解釋更加令人懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會是瞄準我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是來幹什麼的啊 那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該不會有那麼笨的刺客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.88,0:17:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是趕來救我們的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.57,0:18:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯...是那麼打算的但卻反過來被救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是人類居然救擬煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人類也好擬煌珠也好不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 所以不要那麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.23,0:18:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我對於酷是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 和我同契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙的弱點是嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不可思議 比起昨天感覺好很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多謝誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 為什麼會一下子好這麼多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不知道到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.59,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我到最後還在懷疑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係 我已經不放在心上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.37,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託她暫時當一段時間的嚮導怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.96,0:20:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確 有嚮導的話就不用遇到今天這樣的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.42,0:20:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 自從菲蘿走了後感覺異常安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣 能做我們的嚮導嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然 我很榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.59,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過沒有嚮導費哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才還在道歉 一提到錢就這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.50,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 明天開始請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再加把勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.44,0:21:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的這裏稍微有點熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.59,0:22:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會喜歡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.95,0:22:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明知道是沒有希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下回 碎石的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.81,0:23:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第十九唱 碎石的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.49,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此 少女的笑容是真實的

